OL,3,CTrust in water companies plunges to
OL,4,Cnew low amid soaring household bills
OL,6,FTrust in water companies across
OL,7,FEngland and Wales has plunged to a new
OL,8,Flow as households grapple with soaring
OL,9,Fbills, an annual survey has found.
OL,11,FSome 13 water companies saw their
OL,12,Fcustomer trust ratings fall during the
OL,13,Fyear and the overall score for England
OL,14,Fand Wales drop from 6.28 to 6.07 out
OL,15,Fof 10, according to the 15th Water
OL,16,FMatters report by the Consumer Council
OL,17,Ffor Water (CCW).
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
