OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1778753279
OL,3,CTrust in water companies plunges to
OL,4,Cnew low amid soaring household bills
OL,6,FThe most trusted water company was
OL,7,FNorthumbrian Water, which achieved
OL,8,F7.02, while Thames Water was the least
OL,9,Ftrusted with a score of 4.74.
OL,11,FA third of customers (35%) are
OL,12,Fsatisfied with companies' efforts to
OL,13,Fprotect the environment, while
OL,14,Fsatisfaction with sewerage services
OL,15,Fslumped 4% to its lowest ever level of
OL,16,F60%.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
