OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1778753279
OL,3,CTrust in water companies plunges to
OL,4,Cnew low amid soaring household bills
OL,6,FMost common concerns were about
OL,7,Fcompanies' management of sewer
OL,8,Fflooding and their efforts to clean
OL,9,Fwastewater properly before releasing
OL,10,Fit back into the environment.
OL,12,FThe survey also found some 44% of
OL,13,Fhousehold customers believe their
OL,14,Fwater charges are fair, falling for a
OL,15,Fthird successive year to reach another
OL,16,Frecord low.
OL,18,FSome 63% of customers say their water
OL,19,Fbill is affordable, down 11% to
OL,20,Fanother new low.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
