OL,3,CTrust in water companies plunges to
OL,4,Cnew low amid soaring household bills
OL,6,FThe report comes against a backdrop of
OL,7,Funprecedented bill rises in April.
OL,9,FFewer than half of customers (46%)
OL,10,Fsaid their water company was doing a
OL,11,Fgood job of communicating its plans,
OL,12,Fslipping to its lowest ever level,
OL,13,Fdespite firms investing more than #100
OL,14,Fbillion as part of a five-year package
OL,15,Fto improve services and clean up
OL,16,Frivers, streams, lakes and seas.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
