OL,3,CTrust in water companies plunges to
OL,4,Cnew low amid soaring household bills
OL,6,FQueries about bills remained the most
OL,7,Fcommon reason for households to
OL,8,Fcontact their water company ` reaching
OL,9,Fa record high ` but satisfaction with
OL,10,Fcustomer service hit a new low.
OL,12,FThis was also reflected in the number
OL,13,Fof complaints that were escalated to
OL,14,FCCW last year, with the watchdog
OL,15,Fhandling just over 16,000 ` an overall
OL,16,Fincrease of 51% compared with 2024.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
