OL,3,CTrust in water companies plunges to
OL,4,Cnew low amid soaring household bills
OL,6,FCCW chief executive Mike Keil said:
OL,7,F"Fewer customers think they are
OL,8,Fgetting a fair deal or value for money
OL,9,Fand what's clear from our work with
OL,10,Fconsumers is that people want more
OL,11,Fclarity about their bills, how their
OL,12,Fmoney is being spent and what support
OL,13,Fwater companies can offer them."
OL,15,FA Water UK spokesman said: "According
OL,16,Fto this report, 86% of customers are
OL,17,Fsatisfied with their water supply, and
OL,18,Fawareness of the support available to
OL,19,Fhouseholds is at an all-time high.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@`O]wD@\OU
