OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1778753279
OL,3,CTrust in water companies plunges to
OL,4,Cnew low amid soaring household bills
OL,6,F"Water companies are investing a
OL,7,Frecord #104 billion to secure our
OL,8,Fwater supplies, support economic
OL,9,Fgrowth and end sewage entering our
OL,10,Frivers and seas. At the same time,
OL,11,Faround three million households will
OL,12,Freceive reduced bills and other forms
OL,13,Fof financial support by the end of the
OL,14,Fdecade."
